title: Bobby Brings In His Dog Into New Studio + Amy Got Lost In The Woods + How Everyone Almost Died on Vacation
itunes:title: Bobby Brings In His Dog Into New Studio + Amy Got Lost In The Woods + How Everyone Almost Died on Vacation
description:
The show is back from vacay! Bobby brings in his new puppy Stanley to meet the show. Amy talks about how she got lost for 2 hours in the woods. And Bobby gets updates from everyone's stories from vacation. Chris Janson also stops by to break in the new studio!
